org.apache.archiva.repository

Interface ManagedRepository

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventSource, Repository, RepositoryStorage
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EditableManagedRepository
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractManagedRepository, BasicManagedRepository, MavenManagedRepository

    public interface ManagedRepository
extends Repository
    Represents a managed repository, that is readable and writable.
